        The matrix shifted as the oracal came into view. "The war on past earth is going nowhere. We must choos a spark that will help us in out journey." A spark glowed intentavly almost impetuous to return to the world. "You are not one who would add this jorney. Your spark is corrupt. But i may be able to change that."

        The spark  was cleanesed by the oracal. "Go now Maximal Galvatron. you might like being on the side of good for a change." The spark entered the new body built by the oracal itself. "This should do. now be gone" And in that instent Galvatron found himself back on Earth.
